        {
            "id": 6397467,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 恆生科技指數下跌-147.8點至4775.14點，跌幅3%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間26日01:25，恆生科技指數下跌147.8點（或3%），暫報4775.14點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-3.63%</li><li>近 1 月：-6.42%</li><li>近 3 月：-10.48%</li><li>近 6 月：-22.83%</li><li>今年以來：-10.75%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>禽畜肉類概念領跌-6.52%。其中    惠生國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01340:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01340\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01340-HK</a>)            下跌        16.33%            ;        雨潤食品(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01068:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01068\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01068-HK</a>)            下跌        8.62%            ;        中糧家佳康(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01610:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01610\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01610-HK</a>)            下跌        5%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>採購及供應鏈管理概念領跌-4.72%。其中    中遠海運國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00517:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00517\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00517-HK</a>)            下跌        6.28%            ;        卓爾智聯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02098:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02098\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02098-HK</a>)            下跌        5.26%            ;        百德國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02668:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02668\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02668-HK</a>)            下跌        2.9%    。</p></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6397467",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-26 13:40:55",
